Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然向我银之链金术师朱利欧·科曼契挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胆量值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只是擦到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只擦到一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷 您回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫张梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}东方的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次倒在路边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的主人 尤基大人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果好了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来治疗伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是流传于清国的链丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清国？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一个人穿越了东边的大沙漠来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个人和一只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只是指那个小东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 它叫小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是链丹术吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探索流动于大地的力量——龙脉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且运用它的法术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刺青结合了我国链丹术的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥不仅研究了链丹术 还研究了链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刺青就是研究的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥是个非常优秀的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤也治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能毫无牵挂地去中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 马上就准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是叫你快点离开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的不老不死什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 我就是为此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 小鬼就要像个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用链丹术是无法实现不老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是链金术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须去拜见传说中的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发加金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的大衣 飒爽地披在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华丽地拯救人们的天才链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·爱力克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 黑色疾风号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚一个人走路可是很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会被我剁碎手巴利袭击的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 为什么没有反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为认识一个类似的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似？是叫阿尔冯斯什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识阿尔冯斯君？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那家伙的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到第五研究所和制造石头有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 说不定和军队上层也有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及名叫拉斯多和恩维的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们把你变成这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是研究人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们强制把我的灵魂拖了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果调查那些研究者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能查出下令做研究的人是什么来历
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也被作为石头的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封口兼做材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一点都不浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否已经没有必要再制造石头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后再问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个多月前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央都市的电话亭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了一个军队将校的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙被切开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 温莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你今天心情愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘现在都在认真工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了偷盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在靠修理房顶之类的工作来生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 就是稍微绕了点远路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是逐渐地进展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 紧急处理完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在零件不够 先这样将就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就调集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们随便走走打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里只有机械铠店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 捡了只猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说要请你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么小气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许说“小”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在异国遇见的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在异国？你是外国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 从清国来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指那个东边的大国？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越沙漠真是非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要走这种路线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想看看克塞鲁克塞斯遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克塞鲁克塞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调查点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这个国家也是为了调查链丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链丹术？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家叫它链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的国家叫它链丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在医学方面的顶尖技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的国情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里大多用于军事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也和南边的阿耶鲁戈 西边的古雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在国境线附近总是有小冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方也是有大国德拉古马存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说缔结了互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为布里克斯山挡在中间而不攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系也很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个危险的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把链金术广泛用于军事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是现在的大总统布拉德雷上任以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们也很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有顶尖医学水平的链丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你们是链金术师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的弟弟 阿尔冯斯·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细地说说链丹术的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是链丹术师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是术师来调查什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会不会知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来知道些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想用贤者之石做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它获得不老不死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊 说什么不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何 我可不觉得这是有求于人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙会轻功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清国的体术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起师傅来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 追加甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么贤者之石 不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个狐狸眼混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 在我骂那个狐狸眼混蛋之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 基本上猜得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉不到那个铠甲里有活人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得增加人数就有办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下就这点水平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫麟的混蛋也就这点程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 这家伙在主人被辱駡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就失去冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击变得单纯而且动作也大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么差不多让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到是义肢内藏炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不能轻视这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的话 也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链丹术？居然不用阵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…哥哥也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被麟大人骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大街上居然用这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了其他人的话 早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 自己把手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常追兔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱可是我的拿手好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 居然像没事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 做我的部下统治一个国家如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回清…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然把城市弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭钱拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭钱和赔偿由这小子和他的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说这个国家的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 给我站住 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了 说是修好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在这副样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 哥哥 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要链成阵就能链成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为真理的记忆恢复了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（天平左：链金水平 哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（天平右：身高）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威严）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好意思喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过份 我们明明是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那两个人 我可是遇到了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会好好教训他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩叫兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子叫胡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们家族世代侍奉我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭饭吃的家伙居然有两个随从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 我也算是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不都吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种倒在路边向人蹭饭的家伙居然是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许说麟大人的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实一点都不显得身份高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇子也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清国是由50个民族聚集起来组成的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由皇帝统治全国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 各民族领袖的女儿嫁给皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生下小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的皇帝有二十四位皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和十九位皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这其中的第十二位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四十三个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会为了继承权而产生纠纷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就面临这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝的身体状况非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个民族都为了攀上皇位而不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不老不死的方法为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攀上皇位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于贤者之石的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石不是发迹的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉我的话 就一直跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大街上好像出了乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回来晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你总是 总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主没必要给下面的人低头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我低个头就能解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算很便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可关系到姚族50万人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空管这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次准备到哪里去弄坏机械铠？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄坏为前提吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去中央都市调查点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去中央都市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去 想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休斯家道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 温莉有工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也需要放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 伽菲尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家就一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去中央都市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待 中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你不要跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是跟来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 还没问过老爷的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将自己的名字作为神赐的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满怀自豪地称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是 老爷肯定也有个非常自豪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把名字舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是有去无回的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就舍弃全部神赐之物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中充满对再会的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到中央都市的爱德等人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接他们的是悲伤的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 黑暗选出了新的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第16话 战友的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出行的男人心中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光明还是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:23.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:29.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:47.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:59.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:01.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:06.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:13.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:22.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:31.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:43.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:34.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:38.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:45.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:50.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:56.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:58.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:09.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:17.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:23.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:28.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:33.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:45.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:49.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:53.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远

